body.p: The model reproduces Fig 6 of the paper. The stoichiometry and rate of reactions involving uptake of metabolites from extracellular medium have been changed corresponding to Yvol (ratio of extracellular volume to cytosolic volume) mentioned in the publication. The extracellular and cytosolic compartments have been set to 1. Concentration of extracellular glucose, GlcX, is set to 6.7 according to the equation for cellular glucose uptake rate in Table 7 of the paper. The model was successfully tested on MathSBML and Jarnac
